{{> /common/header }}
	<div class="my-2 p-2">
		<h2>로그인</h2>
	</div>
	{{#error}}
		<div class="alert alert-danger alert-dismissible" role="alert">
			아이디 혹은 비밀번호가 일치하지 않습니다.
			<button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="alert" aria-label="Close"></button>
		</div>
	{{/error}}
	<form action="/user/login" method="post">
		<div class="my-2 p-2">
			<label class="form-labal">아이디</label>
			<input type="text" name="loginId" class="form-control" value="{{#data.loginId}}{{.}}{{/data.loginId}}"/>
		</div>
		<div class="my-2 p-2">
			<label class="form-labal">비밀번호</label>
			<input type="password" name="loginPass" class="form-control"/>
		</div>
		<div class="my-2 p-2">
		<button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">로그인</button>
		</div>
	</form>
	<div class="my-2 p-2">
		아이디가 없으십니까? <a href="/user/join" style="text-decoration: none;">회원가입</a>을 하고 모임에 참가해보세요!
	</div>
{{> /common/footer }}